description:
Duker is a captain in the Zanscare Empire`s Motorad Squadron. Initially he deploys using some of the Zanscare combat bike to attack the League Millitare. His significance in the story grows until he eventually becomes the one to suggest the Adrastea class ship and deployment of the Motorad Squadron. By the end of the series he has command of a Lysithea class cruiser.
Source: gundam.wikia.com
name: Duker Iq
